<br>Scalp massages are a great way to enhance your relaxation. In fact, <a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5088109/" target="_self" style="color: rgb(222, 171, 91);">a 2016 study</a> found that scalp massages can also help to lower blood pressure and reduce levels of the stress hormone cortisol. <br>
<br>When you combine a scalp massage with aromatherapy, you can help to stimulate hair growth, nourish your hair and ease any headaches and tension. <br>
